gomodel:SYNGO_2208  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0099026 replaced by GO:0042734" , "Rationale: GPC4/VGlut1-positive puncta were juxtaposed to PSD-95 puncta, suggesting that GPC4 also localizes to excitatory presynaptic terminals in vivo. GPC4 showed little colocalization with the pre- and postsynaptic inhibitory markers VGAT and gephyrin.\n\n28/12/2017 Pim\n- Based on the lipid anchor of the protein, the \"anchored component of ... membrane\" term was chosen.. Experimental description: Experimental Procedures\nImmunohistochemistry\nAcute parasagittal slices were cut from P15-21 rat brains.\n\n28/12/2017 Pim\n- Overexpressed protein is of mouse species: \"We expressed HA-tagged mouse cDNAs for these glypican...\"" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5518-6584" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-6194-9648" ;
        dc:date           "2024-03-14" ;
        dc:title          "SYNGO_CC_2208" ;
        pav:providedBy    "https://syngo.vu.nl" ;
        biolink:in_taxon  "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/NCBITaxon_10116" .

